%%{init: {'theme':'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Op as Operator
    participant SPA as SPA (calibration.js)
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>(mover_calibrator.py)
    participant DMX as Art-Net bridge<br/>(DMX fixture)
    participant Cam as Camera node<br/>(camera_server.py)

    Op->>SPA: Click Start Calibration
    SPA->>Orch: POST /api/calibration/mover/{fid}/start
    Orch->>Orch: _set_calibrating(fid, True)<br/>(engine stops pan/tilt writes)

    Note over Orch,DMX: Warmup (~30s)
    loop each warmup sweep step
        Orch->>DMX: _hold_dmx(pan,tilt,colour)
    end

    Note over Orch,Cam: Discovery (~45-55s)
    loop battleship grid or coarse 10x7
        Orch->>DMX: set pan,tilt
        Orch->>Cam: POST /beam-detect
        Cam-->>Orch: pixel or null
    end
    opt beam found (battleship)
        Orch->>DMX: pan + nudge
        Orch->>Cam: POST /beam-detect
        Orch->>DMX: tilt + nudge
        Orch->>Cam: POST /beam-detect
        Note right of Orch: #658 blink-confirm<br/>rejects reflections
    end

    Note over Orch,Cam: Mapping / Convergence (~35-50s)
    loop BFS or per-target converge
        Orch->>DMX: set pan,tilt
        Orch->>Cam: POST /beam-detect<br/>(dual-capture, #655)
        Cam-->>Orch: pixel median
    end

    Note over Orch: Grid build (<1s, sync)
    Note over Orch,Cam: Verification sweep (3-5s)
    loop 3 held-out points
        Orch->>DMX: set pan,tilt
        Orch->>Cam: POST /beam-detect
    end

    Note over Orch: LM fit — try 4 sign combos
    Note over Orch,DMX: Sign verification probes
    Orch->>DMX: pan + delta
    Orch->>Cam: /beam-detect
    Orch->>DMX: tilt + delta
    Orch->>Cam: /beam-detect

    Note over Orch,Cam: Held-out parametric gate (#654)
    Orch->>DMX: set pan,tilt (unseen target)
    Orch->>Cam: /beam-detect
    Orch-->>SPA: verify RMS in status

    alt RMS within tolerance
        Orch->>Orch: fixture.moverCalibrated=true
        Orch->>Orch: _save("fixtures")
        Orch-->>SPA: status=done
    else RMS too high
        Orch-->>SPA: prompt Accept/Retry
    end

    Orch->>DMX: blackout
    Orch->>Orch: _set_calibrating(fid, False)
    SPA-->>Op: complete

    Note over Op,Orch: On cancel at any phase
    Op->>SPA: Cancel
    SPA->>Orch: POST /cancel
    Orch->>DMX: immediate zero (foreground)
    Orch->>Orch: _cancel_event.set()<br/>background raises<br/>CalibrationAborted
    Orch->>Orch: _cal_blackout()<br/>release claim
